quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  7,130,"Gom…óii Men nanngirii yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen kokke e …óuytagol dim…óe ; belajo'o, …ìe waajitoto"
  7,131,"Si mo∆¥∆¥ere nden arii …ìe, …ìe wi'a : \"Me…óen hanndi e ndee …óoo\" ; si bone on he…ìii …ìe, …ìe kiitinora Muusaa e wonndu…ìe e makko …ìen. Anndee pellet, kiiti ma…ì…ìe …óin ko ka Alla iwri, kono ko …ìuri …óuu…óude e yim…ìe …ìen anndaa"
  7,132,"∆Åe wi'i : \"Kala ko addan …óaa …ìen e Aayaa fii no mbil…óoraa men …óum ; men wonaali gom…óinoo…ìe ma"
  7,133,"Men wurti e ma…ì…ìe waame, e kanu, e karan=tendi, e totiiji=paabi, e ∆¥ii∆¥am, ko Aayeeje fensitaa…óe, …ìe mawnintinii, …ìe laatii yim…ìe bom…ìe"
  7,134,"Tuma nde lepte …óen yanunoo e ma…ì…ìe, …ìe wi'i : \"ko an Muusaa, torano men Joomi maa sabu kon ko O ahodi e maa…óa. Si a huncanii men …óee lepte, ma men gom…óine, ma men accide kadi e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen"
  7,135,"Nde Men huncannoo …ìe lepte …óen haa e lajal ngal …ìe yottotoo, jaka yoo kam…ìe ko …ìe firtoo…ìe (ahadi ma…ì…ìe ndin)"
  7,136,"Men yottii e ma…ì…ìe ; Men yooliri …ìe ka maayo sabu ko …ìe fenniri kon Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìe laatii welsindii…ìe e majje"
  7,137,"Men ronini yim…ìe wonanoo…ìe lo'ineede …ìen fu…ónaange leydi ndin e hiirnaange mayri ndi Men barkini e mu'un. Konngol Joomi maa mo∆¥∆¥ongol ngol timmii e …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen sabu ko …ìe mu√±√±inoo kon. Men halki ko Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun …ìen mo∆¥∆¥inanynoo, e kon ko …ìe …ìamtaynoo (e ku…ìeeje)"
  7,138,"Men lummbini …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen maayo ngon, …ìe rewi ka yim…ìe √±ii…ìu…ìe (e rewugol) sanamuuji mu'un, …ìe wi'i : \"Ko an yo Muusaa, wa…óan men rewetee…óo wano rewetee…ói woodirani …ìe non\". O maaki : \"Pellet, onon ko on yim…ìe majjoo…ìe"
  7,139,"Pellet, …ìee …óoo, ko …ìe woni e mun kon ko halkaa…óum, kadi ko mere woni ko …ìe gollaynoo"
  7,140,"E ko ko woori Alla mi …óa…ì…ìanta on rewetee…óo, Kanko O …ìurnii on e Winndere nden"
  7,141,"(Annditee) tuma nde Men da…óndunoo on e yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen, hi…ìe mee…óina on lepte bon…óe : …ìe wara …ìi…ó…ìe mon wor…ìe …ìe heddina rew…ìe mon …ìen. No e …óum moo…óon jarrabuyee maw…óo immorde ka Joomi mon"